data.description: Step into your perfect retreat! Begin your day with breathtaking sunrises on the expansive covered front porch. This home features a wood burning fireplace and a spacious kitchen that boasts ample cabinets for storage. Out the back a large deck and fire pit become your go-to spot for entertaining. Spread across 5 acres, indulge in livestock, gardens, and endless fun. The property also features a charming pond. An ideal haven for those seeking a beautiful home with abundant space for all their aspirations.*This is NOT a manufactured mobile home.*
